HowTo Run BiToo

0)Dependencies

put in your CLASSPATH:

Azureus2.jar, from Azureus-2.2.0.0 ( http://azureus.sf.net/ )
log4j-1.2.9.jar, from ( http://logging.apache.org/log4j/docs/ )
commons-cli-1.0.jar, from ( http://jakarta.apache.org/commons/cli/ )

1)Build from source

Require ant from ( http://ant.apache.org/ )

To build run ant in this same directory, jar will be put in dist/lib/ directory

2)Run

Configure the properties file etc/bitoo.properties

Choose a client adapter, for now AzureusWebUI ( http://azureus.sourceforge.net/plugin_details.php?plugin=webui )
and original BitTorrent ( http://bittorrent.com/ ) are supported.
